text: René Pinchart (24 June 1891 - 2 November 1970) was a Belgian gymnast. He competed in the men's team, Swedish system event at the 1920 Summer Olympics, winning the bronze medal. ==References== Category:1891 births Category:1970 deaths Category:Belgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belgium Category:Gymnasts at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Belgium Category:Medalists at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic medalists in gymnastics Category:People from Maldegem
